{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/blog/design/css-layout","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Layout 잘 만들기!</h1>\n<p>css 중에 layout쪽이라도 잘하면 좋을것 같아서 정리해본다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>position, flex, grid를 위주로 정리해봄</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>What is Viewport</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Viewport_concepts\">Viewport Concepts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JANETBQZJ8E&#x26;ab_channel=TheNetNinja\">Responsive Web Design Tutorial #3 - Intro to the Viewport</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://web.dev/viewport/#:~:text=Without%20a%20viewport%20meta%20tag,sized%20correctly%20on%20all%20devices.\">Viewport meta tag</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Viewport_meta_tag\">mdn using the viewport meta tag to control layout on mobile browsers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://aboooks.tistory.com/352\">meta viewport 사용법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@nids.nitesh/understanding-the-viewport-meta-tag-b5ccd8c4f0e6\">understanding the viewport meta tag</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6333927/difference-between-visual-viewport-and-layout-viewport#:~:text=The%20visual%20viewport%20is%20the,not%20change%20size%20or%20shape.\">Difference between visual viewport and layout viewport?</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>UTF-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">http-equiv</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>X-UA-Compatible<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>IE=edge<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- &lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"> --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>viewport<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>width=960, initial-scale=1.0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- initial-scale은 zoom level --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Document<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=960, initial-scale=1.0\" /> 일때 \n      width:320px로 주면 모바일 디바이스의 너비가 320px이라도 960px이 너비라고 기준을 잡고 \n      그린다음 크기를 여기에 맞춰버린다.   */</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 320px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bisque<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>app<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h1>media query</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\">media query</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/CSS_layout/Media_queries\">beginner's guide to media query</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* desktop first */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Media Queries */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@mediq</span> screen <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 700px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">footer</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/* something */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://kinsta.com/blog/responsive-web-design/\">The Beginner’s Guide to Responsive Web Design (Code Samples &#x26; Layout Examples)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://devfacts.com/media-queries-breakpoints-2021/\">Media Queries Breakpoints For Responsive Design In 2021</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>rem px em differences</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://chiamakaikeanyi.dev/sizing-in-css-px-vs-em-vs-rem/#:~:text=px%20is%20not%20scalable%2C%20it%20is%20an%20absolute%20unit.&#x26;text=Element%20(%20em%20)%20and%20Root%20element,the%20value%20of%20relative%20units\">https://chiamakaikeanyi.dev/sizing-in-css-px-vs-em-vs-rem/#:~:text=px%20is%20not%20scalable%2C%20it%20is%20an%20absolute%20unit.&#x26;text=Element%20(%20em%20)%20and%20Root%20element,the%20value%20of%20relative%20units</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%ED%95%B4%EC%83%81%EB%8F%84\">What’s The Difference Between PX, EM, REM, %, VW, and VH?</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>resolution</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%ED%95%B4%EC%83%81%EB%8F%84\">https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%ED%95%B4%EC%83%81%EB%8F%84</a></p>\n<h1>what is fluid layout</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>FLUID layouts use relative measurements and respond to the width of the viewport. FIXED layouts use static measurements and do not respond to the width of the viewport.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>Understanding CSS Layout</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/CSS_layout\">css layout</a></li>\n<li>float, postion, flex, grid</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Responsive Site</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3tLb3i7GB38&#x26;list=PL4cUxeGkcC9g9Vh9MAA-XKnfJsWZnPZFw&#x26;ab_channel=TheNetNinja\">what is responsive web design</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bn-DQCifeQQ&#x26;ab_channel=KevinPowell\">Responsive design made easy</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Apply responsive design</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hayoung0Lee/gatsby-gomtang\">my repo</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>responsive image</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LlSH8u0o1-A&#x26;list=PL4cUxeGkcC9g9Vh9MAA-XKnfJsWZnPZFw&#x26;index=10&#x26;ab_channel=TheNetNinja\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LlSH8u0o1-A&#x26;list=PL4cUxeGkcC9g9Vh9MAA-XKnfJsWZnPZFw&#x26;index=10&#x26;ab_channel=TheNetNinja</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>web design for developers</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://thenewstack.io/tutorial-web-design-101-for-web-developers/\">web design for developers</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ykn4XNDwW7Q&#x26;ab_channel=KevinPowell\">web design for developers youtube</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>make clear blocks using rem and stuff</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Fixing layouts</h1>\n<p>1.</p>\n<h1>References</h1>","frontmatter":{"date":"April 01, 2021","slug":"/blog/design/css-layout","title":"Css Layout"}}},"pageContext":{"birthTime":"2021-04-02T14:01:33.515Z","modifiedTime":"2021-04-02T14:01:33.515Z","slug":"/blog/design/css-layout"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1947816842"]}